      "label": "Display work",
      "headline": "Displays that work before they are built.",
      "intro": "A display has to do more than look good. Working in 3D makes it possible to test product fit, proportion, material, sightlines, and service details before the object moves into production. It gives the team a clear way to judge how the piece will hold product, support service, and read in the real world.",
      "lanes": [
